text: Mohamed Yunus al-Menfi (; born March 3, 1976) is a Libyan politician. On 5 February 2021, he was chosen to be the president of the Libyan Presidential Council at the Libyan Political Dialogue Forum. He was the Libyan Ambassador to Greece. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Heads of state of Libya Category:Ambassadors of Libya Category:Current national leaders
